<div class="hero hero-sm">
  <div>
    <h1>{{page.title}}</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="wrapper">
  <section>
    <div class="card mb-6">
      <p class="m-0 fw-500">Grant the admin role to {{content.displayName}}?</p>
      {{#if content.tierLabel}}
        <p class="m-0 mt-1 text-muted">Current membership: {{content.tierLabel}}</p>
      {{/if}}
      <p class="m-0 mt-1 text-muted">Reason: {{content.reason}}</p>
    </div>

    <p>This grants the platform admin role, subscribes the member to the admin-alerts list, and emails them. They will then be able to manage members, the work queue, and other administrators.</p>

    <form method="POST" action="{{content.confirmHref}}">
      <input type="hidden" name="member_key" value="{{content.memberKey}}" />
      <input type="hidden" name="reason" value="{{content.reason}}" />
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Yes, Grant the Admin Role</button>
    </form>

    <p class="mt-4"><a href="{{content.cancelHref}}">Cancel</a></p>
  </section>
</div>
